The paper focuses on the integration of computer vision and language processing in machine translation, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), or machine learning (cs.LG). The use of reinforcement learning as the main algorithm also suggests that it could belong to the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or information retrieval (cs.IR).
